pos_mean_info_list.mean: [胚] 性别；性欲；性征；性方面的事情（比如性行为或性能力）

word_group.brief_definition: 性活动；性生活；性爱活动

bilingual.target: 这本书探讨了性的身份认同。
这部电影包含一些性的内容。

bilingual.source: They had a discussion about sexual health.
bilingual.target: 他们讨论了性的健康问题。

bilingual.source: He was uncomfortable with the sexual jokes.
bilingual.target: 他对那些性的笑话感到不舒服。
性的教育对青少年很重要。

bilingual.source: They fail to create proper sexual tension.
bilingual.target: 他们没有打造合适的性的吸引力。

bilingual.source: Sexual incompatibility is wide-spread in the apple.
bilingual.target: 性的不亲合性在苹果中很普遍。

bilingual.source: I want you to enjoy your sexual and erotic power.
bilingual.target: 我希望你感受性的力量；

bilingual.source: With Strickland the sexual appetite took a very small place.
bilingual.target: 性的饥渴在思特里克兰德身上占的地位很小。

bilingual.source: What about the other side of this contrast? Sexual orientation.
bilingual.target: 我们接着谈另一个问题：性的取向。

yingyinNormal.en: Women are required to dress in a way that does not attract sexual attention.
yingyinNormal.zh: "女性的穿着不能对他人具有性吸引力"。

yingyinNormal.en: Low self-esteem. Social anxiety. Sexual insecurity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自尊低落。社交焦虑。性生活不安全感。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, granted, Penny, your secondary sexual characteristics are reasonably bodacious.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩妮，虽然你的第二性征相当明显。

yingyinNormal.en: And this was a sexual case, too? Yes, prostitution. Lockhart/Gardner just seems to obsess on these sexual cases.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这也是个性犯罪案件吗？是的，卖淫案。洛&加律所似乎对性犯罪案件很着迷。

yingyinNormal.en: Sure. Sure, I'll just sit next to the trans-sexual from purchasing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，是啊，我会坐在采购部那个变性人旁边。

yingyinNormal.en: We expected them to be conservative in the sexual preferences and they were.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们也预测他们的性偏好会较为保守，事实与预测一致。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, nothing happen. You could cut the sexual tension in here with a knife.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，没跟他亲热，刚才的情欲张力一触即发。

yingyinNormal.en: We still have you in your office conducting sexual relations with underlings.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们还有你在办公室和下属有过性行为的牌没打呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Now it also says here that you lied about your sexual preference before marriage?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这上面还说你在婚前隐瞒性向。

yingyinNormal.en: You mean sexual intercourse? Well, when you say it like that you make it sound creepy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是指性爱？你这么一说，就显得怪怪的。

yingyinNormal.en: You can imagine studying in many situations. We chose sexual arousal, so what did we do?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们可以研究不同情况的双重人格，我们选择性兴奋状态作变量，我们的研究是怎样进行的呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Now given that winter is coming, one can only assume she's signaling sexual availability.
yingyinNormal.zh: 既然冬天都已经到了，只能说明她是在暗示，她可以作为做爱对象。

yingyinNormal.en: They keep throwing sexual harassment cases at me and I keep knocking them out of the park!
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们一直把性骚扰案丢给我，我一直把他们打得毫无退路。

yingyinNormal.en: Last night, I was feeling in need of sexual release when I happened to come across your mother.
yingyinNormal.zh: 昨晚我有释放性需求的感觉时，恰好想到你的母亲。

yingyinNormal.en: Their sexual pics and the prostitution scandals are all as a disgrace to the country and its people.
yingyinNormal.zh: 更有甚者，被曝光丑闻，让人民简直不忍直视。

yingyinNormal.en: And we ask them questions. We ask them questions about the sexual preferences, the whole list of things.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们问他们一些问题，一些与性爱偏好有关的问题，一整页与之有关的问题。

yingyinNormal.en: And over the last year, I've dedicated myself to sexual assault reform, and have made meaningful strides.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而去年一年，我都致力于性侵法案改革，已经取得可喜进展。

yingyinNormal.en: There are pitfalls. Trust me, I know. When it comes to sexual harassment law, I'm a bit of a self taught expert.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这有隐患，相信我，我清楚，说到性骚扰的相关法律，我可是自学而成的专家。

yingyinNormal.en: What? You wanna see me self-defend myself? Go over there and pretend you're a sexual predator. Go on. I dare you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想试试我的防身术吗？现在就假装你是性侵犯者，有种就去。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, should you have any interaction with her, it would be most helpful that she not see you as a sexual rival.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而且你应该多和她接触一下，好让她别感觉到你是她的性竞争对手。
